desc: Butchery & Farm Shop is set on Cheshire farmland boasting various livestock. Experienced craft butchers offer traditional service & advice on all things meat, BBQ & Steak. Local, top quality meat & other produce. Cheshire's 1st Himalayan Salt Chamber for perfectly ageing Cheshires finest steak. Visit us or buy online!

layout.text: SK Ten Farm Shop & Online Butchery

We supply Cheshire’s finest prime beef, pork, lamb and poultry, with game available during the season. Proudly regarded as one of the UK’s best meat suppliers, as all of our meat is free range and reared on our own land at Cherry Tree Farm, or is locally sourced, meaning we can provide a fabulous quality product at a great price.

Buy with confidence - we deliver anywhere in the UK.
